data.description: Wonderful Rambler on huge corner lot! Check out this 4 bdrm, 2 bath with a 2 car detached garage. Alongside the garage is a 62X19 area for extra car parking. A newly built shed is 16X6.5 and new deck on front entrance to the home. Backyard has a privacy fence around the entire yard with nice landscaping, a gardener's delight, apple trees, cherry tree and an entertainment area with firepit. House is updated with new paint, new flooring throughout, new kitchen appliances. Tons of potential in the basement complete with 1 bedroom, family room, bonus room, laundry, roughed in bath with floor and ceiling complete and extra space for storage. Don't miss out on this wonderful home that you can make yours today!
